  <scopecontent id="aspace_bcedd77bf1998f06bce0f03b5b2a3375">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Memorabilia, prints, scrapbooks, photographs and lantern slides of field trips, and meeting minutes related to the Dept. of Botany.</p><p> Photographs, including some of Barbara McClintock and Karl Wiegand; scrapbooks belonging to Professors Muenscher and Knudson; and diaries belonging to Professor Walter Muenscher.</p>  </scopecontent>
